timing_disable...removal_checks(25.10)  timing_disable...removal_checks(25.10)

Name
       timing_disable_recovery_removal_checks

Syntax
       timing_disable_recovery_removal_checks

       {true | false}

       Default: false (performs checks)

       When  set  to  true,  disables recovery and removal timing model checks
       during timing analysis.

       To set this global variable, use the set_global command.

